### Get all customers (distinct vevo names)
GET http://localhost:3000/vevok

###

### Get customer transactions by vevo name
GET http://localhost:3000/vevok/Kovacs Janos

###

### Create new transaction with customer
POST http://localhost:3000/vevok
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "termek": "Hotdog",
  "vevo": "Kovacs Janos",
  "kategoriaId": 1,
  "egyseg": "db",
  "nettoar": 800,
  "mennyiseg": 2,
  "kiadva": true
}

